{"type": "article", "id": 52944, "title": "Nike 起诉 Puma 侵权，以及，Met Gala 开始了 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-05-08T03:22:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 47724, "name": "G-SHOCK"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 44164, "name": "Puma"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 9688, "name": "Met Gala"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180508111314W6ZfhqbXcEK14gpQ.png", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/watches/karl-lagerfeld-watch-licensing-deal-swarovski-fossil-1202667584/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Karl Lagerfeld 和 Swarovski 签订手表合同</strong></a> | 周一，老佛爷同名品牌 Karl Lagerfeld 与 Swarovski 正式签订多年的手表合同，生产一系列男女款手表。此前，Karl Lagerfeld 品牌手表由 Fossil 授权生产。截止至去年年底，Swarovski 在全球 170 多个国家和地区有近 3000 家门店，年销售额为 27 亿欧元。 </p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Burberry-reviews-use-of-fur-full-ban-likely,975042.html#.WvBS19Nub6Y\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Burberry 正在重新考虑是否使用皮草</strong></a> | 尽管 Burberry 一直以来并非皮草大户，但由于“同行压力”和千禧一代对待皮草的态度转变，Buberry 向 The Sunday Times 证实，正在重新考虑皮草政策。Buberry 没有提出明确的皮草禁令，但相关时尚媒体认为，Buberry 很快就会放弃皮草了。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Nike-sues-Puma-for-copying-Flyknit-shoe,975316.html#.WvDtgiO76LI\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Nike 起诉 Puma 抄袭 Flyknit 鞋</strong></a> | Nike 在美国马萨诸塞州联邦法院提起诉讼，称 Puma “没有得到许可就使用了 Nike 的技术”。根据该诉讼，Nike 在 2012 年推出了 Flyknit，三年后，Puma 开始生产它的 Ignite，Nike 称这是从它的四个注册专利中窃取的技术。Nike 正在寻求永久禁令，以阻止 Puma 继续侵权，并申请损害赔偿。Puma 准备对此诉讼发起抗议，它声称没有侵权行为。</p><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/V6LwhS9Ue6E0W6I-HjcOYQ\" rel=\"nofollow\">前 GQ 编辑总监王锋担任时尚集团副总裁兼首席内容官</a></b> | 据时尚头条网报道，在原时尚集团总裁苏芒离任后，时尚集团在 5 月 8 日早上宣布“自成立以来最重要的一次组织架构调整和高层任命”，其中，王锋—— 前 GQ 主编，被任命为时尚集团副总裁兼首席内容官，这也是该集团第一位首席内容官。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>G-SHOCK 诞生 35 周年，5 月 12 日起，将在东京六本木大厦开展“<a href=\"https://www.wwdjapan.com/607993\" rel=\"nofollow\">G-SHOCK FAN FESTA”。 </a></p><p>活动现场，将会展出多个经典的 G-SHOCK 初代模型，包括 DW-5000C、LOV96-2、FROGMAN、DW-6300 等。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508082842nelNEWoApH2f0MtU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.321586\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>今年九月，Gucci 和 Dapper Dan 将在 Harlem 区开专卖店，双方的合作款，包括一系列服装和配饰，在 5 月 6 日全新开幕的 Wooster Street 63 号的 Gucci 店内率先亮相。来看看： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508082913huzRmaoOUE8rfFS1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508082918QbSeH7zhVPvXojaf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508082918qAXK9HemRztjbSxJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080829206KMkAZ3I4bVQRcYU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/fashion-week/cruise-2019/prada/collection/look/1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada 2019 Cruise 大秀</a>，选在了它的美国总部内。 </p><p>几年前，Prada 买下了曼哈顿的一个旧钢琴厂作为总部。如今，它成了汇聚时髦餐厅和公寓楼的活力社区。建筑事务所 Herzog &amp; de Meuron 用半透明的红色隔板，为 Prada 打造了秀场。 </p><p>这一季 Prada 的灵感大部分都来自于 90 年代——Prada 标志性的饱和色调和几何图案大量出现。Kate Moss 曾戴着一顶 Jean Paul Gaultier 的帽子，为 Harper’s Bazaar 拍摄的照片也成了灵感来源之一，它变成了秀场上引人注目的巨型猎人帽。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083020RYboWGnxhNjKV8w6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050808303534T9SL1gdvIoDQRe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080830152zNvMDgstrO3SGVy.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080830167EjWZ2f93YBRysKP.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083016V8sdtNU6HfIg92YJ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083016THK6JaoqB8ZCpwen.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083016eQy86hsMlWSjazFH.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083017yXiKhzwbp6cMtv1N.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083018upkUm9GiMjAwF4tL.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083018nkJUEX1Qe0BiRGqS.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083018dVIojUFRXwT17mNZ.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083018Px9yRHnILuMKolT6.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080830199n5WIwakFTx0Hr2u.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083020b7RHo64YV5WIDwvt.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083020rGUfMKocHCDyOLtY.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080830206MN0e4gKHf2ZDiYt.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083020hKfZTtHMdVu1nGpy.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201805080830220sdUrPXbkxMimjQ9.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083022eSncJ7PKf5NwhixT.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083022vofZIRk7LFgWB6x1.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083029HG6a43vo9XAcmiUC.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083029mSgOeobKGJ3ivTHV.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083029rFIG7u3ofXjgKOx8.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508083030N7yVYQlO18Pzb4nT.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p class=\"\">Met Gala 2018 “天赐之体：时尚与天主教的想象”（Heavenly Bodies: Fashion and the Catholic Imagination）于美国当地时间 5 月 7 日在纽约大都会艺术博物馆正式开幕。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102752lsx5hwRBLQyUipg6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">Photo: Vogue</figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102752mw3PJX2LD0hIZaOf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102752SJtbw6zF4fy5aROp.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102753h1GpSz7A4FW5yOkX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102753y1W5RrgwnmEuzvK9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805081027548uo650O3UJdEAzNf.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508102754mLa4serh9kIowCBE.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">此次展览与宗教息息相关，而出席慈善晚宴的明星也将在自己的服装上发挥想象力，造型师也从天主教文化和人物中汲取灵感。</p><p class=\"\">目前，<a href=\"https://www.vogue.com/slideshow/met-gala-best-dressed-celebrity-red-carpet-fashion\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"\">Vogue</a> 已经评选出了最佳红毯造型，我们为你选取了一些有意思的（但不限于 Vogue 最佳），来看看他们是如何理解和演绎“时尚与天主教的想象”：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103019jbxrgpliwFMuDhKv.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.457333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Rihanna in custom Masion Margiela by John Galliano All photos: Vogue</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103021t2dwq9CHP3KcAmeS.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Amal Clooney in Richard Quinn</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805081033256F4TJCXf2lYmutiI.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Frances McDormand in Valentino</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103326rmfhLECeuqROkHDG.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Rosie Huntington in Ralph Lauren</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805081033276Wvkqh1ltKmouzNg.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Andreea Diaconu in Chopard Jewelry</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805081033278vHOomgplsuXfhWx.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Zoe Kravitz in Saint Laurent by Anthony Vaccarello</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201805081038006e0GrkEZ42hc95fX.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.150667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Kate Bosworth in Oscar de la Renta</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103759LOmtXQiAonaz7dPx.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Chadwick Boseman in Versace</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103800lTnEWIBCxKFS9diz.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Madonna in Jean Paul Gaultier</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508103759DztemXHa0TqrhobY.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.380000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Katy Perry</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508104412NITwsrRjYVySGuQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504225\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>Anna Wintour in Chanel</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180508104711SG7tBXz5jVQnZ0Fw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>刘雯 in Michael Kors</p></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018050810474858FoOyGIzxAsX4Em.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.685333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">奚梦瑶&nbsp;</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来自：Vogue<br></p>"}